  "bodyHtml": "<p style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">The seller portal is where you can view, update, and follow along with your requests in the SSC</span></span></span></span></span></span><br> </p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"article 8 - image 1.PNG\" src=\"/ssc/servlet/rtaImage?eid=ka0aT000000LzA9&amp;feoid=00N3X00000M5fJO&amp;refid=0EM3X0000084pFI\"></img></h2>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><br><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">How to answer or update my requests?</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">There are two ways to answer SSC requests:</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"> </p>\n<ul><li style=\"line-height: 1.38;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 13px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">After receiving an answer to your initial request, you can follow up via email. To do this, just reply to the email you receive from the SSC. This will also update your case in your portal.</span></span></span></span></span></li><li style=\"line-height: 1.38;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">You can also reply in your portal by adding a comment and clicking “Save”.</span></span></span></span></span></li></ul>\n<p><img class=\"\" alt=\"my request details.PNG\" src=\"/ssc/servlet/rtaImage?eid=ka0aT000000LzA9&amp;feoid=00N3X00000M5fJO&amp;refid=0EM3X000009g8Wa\" style=\"width: 977px;height: 624px;\"></img><br> </p>\n<div id=\"\" style=\"left: 20px;top: 657.95px;\"> </div>"
